The edit review page displays all the information about your review for this paper. You can re-rate each criterion at any time and leave a comment about the individual rating in the comment field to the right of the criterion row. Click the 'recalculate' button to let CoMa recalculate the overall rating of your review. You can also leave an overall comment about the paper in the summary field, and drop some confidential notes for the eyes of the chairs only in the 'confidential notes' field. There is room for your personal remarks in the 'common remarks' field.
Click the 'update review' button when you are finished. If you want to reset the fields, click 'reset review'.
